<collectingCountry id="E4817635FFC8FF8EF58C9CF7F786F793" name="India" pageId="4" pageNumber="309">India</collectingCountry>
(Karnatka). H. e. moerens Wroughton, 1915 — 
<collectingCountry id="E4817635FFC8FF8EF64B9323F7AEF725" name="Bangladesh" pageId="4" pageNumber="309">Bangladesh</collectingCountry>
